profile:
Dos Rios Canada Inc. Is licensed and insured to perform work in your home, office or commercial and industrial locations. Our area of expertise is concrete placement and finishing. Doing concrete work is where we mostly find ourselves; however, finishing interior work is a fine skill present within our workforce. DRC was featured in a few episodes of HGTV, although under a different name -Home Works-    


 Mission Statement
 -To solidly construct every project through workmanship and communication  


 Vision Statement
-Known to respond quickly and efficiently  to every business call. A one-call solution for homeowners and big-name constructors within the GTA.
services: Construction, Home Additions, Footings and Foundations, Concrete Work, Polished Concrete
brands: Sika, Mapei, Husqvarna, QC Concrete Products, Bartell
specialities:
Placement of concrete and finishing
Polished Concrete

profile:
Sprayman Group Installs Commercial & Industrial Interior Flooring Services - The Sprayman Group provides unique flooring protection, renewal and maintenance options resulting in high-quality, attractive and durable finishes.

Sprayman repairs concrete decks, floors, sidewalks, steps and foundations.  We also offer concrete grinding and concrete polishing for all of our residential and commercial customers.

We will contact you within 24 hours of receiving your request.
services:
Concrete repairs; decks, floors, sidewalks, steps and foundations.

Epoxy-type floor coatings for garages, basements, porches, stairs, as well as industrial and commercial settings

Asphalt repairs; cracks, potholes, sealing, line painting, driveway curb repairs (where asphalt meets garage curb), catch basin repairs.
